      The Alfa Laval NX 314 <a href="/decanter-centrifuge/">Decanter Centrifuge</a> is a horizontal de-sludging centrifuge built for the two-phase separation of wastewater, crude oil tank bottoms, municipal sludge-thickening, industrial sludge dewatering, paint sludge handling, etc. With a 10 HP Motor, the NX 314 decanter has a bowl RPM of 4,000 and can process 25 GPM of ethanol hemp biomass slurry.
    </p>


