    <!-- Bare Centrifuge vs Complete Module -->
    <h3 id="bare-centrifuge-vs-complete-module">Bare Centrifuge vs Complete Plug-and-Play Module</h3>

    <p>
      Dolphin Centrifuge can supply an Alfa Laval NX-314 decanter as a loose centrifuge package or as a complete plug-and-play module. The right option depends on what equipment the customer already has on site.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
